24:03.400 --> 24:06.612
Your Serene
Highness, good evening.

24:06.779 --> 24:08.364
Trivial misunderstanding.

24:10.658 --> 24:14.119
Oh, I think it's very clear
what has happened here.

24:24.380 --> 24:29.718
II'

24:55.202 --> 25:00.290
II'

25:12.803 --> 25:13.637
Mr. Penge.

25:13.804 --> 25:15.931
What's that in your wig, boy'?

25:23.814 --> 25:24.940
Sand.

25:28.902 --> 25:29.987
See that.

25:30.154 --> 25:33.490
There is much, much less
than that

25:33.657 --> 25:36.076
between you working here

25:36.243 --> 25:38.454
and you being out
on your thick ear

25:38.620 --> 25:40.706
without a reference.

25:43.834 --> 25:45.753
"Lo!

25:45.919 --> 25:48.088
"We shall not...

25:48.255 --> 25:49.882
"shield..." ALBERT: No, no, no.

25:50.049 --> 25:51.675
"Yield," I think.

25:51.842 --> 25:52.926
Try again.

25:53.093 --> 25:57.139
We shall remain here
until you master it.

25:57.306 --> 25:58.932
It looks like "shield."

25:59.099 --> 26:00.976
How can one letter

26:01.143 --> 26:02.519
look like two'?

26:02.686 --> 26:04.188
"We shall not shield"?

26:04.354 --> 26:05.439
It's stupid.

26:05.606 --> 26:07.149
You're stupid. Bertie.

26:07.316 --> 26:09.026
Concentrate... again -.

26:09.193 --> 26:10.277
It's not fair.

26:10.444 --> 26:12.237
The letters won't stay still.

26:12.404 --> 26:14.114
They're all... swimming.

26:16.617 --> 26:18.994
That is not the behavior
of a future king.

26:19.161 --> 26:20.579
Why can't we do digging?

26:20.746 --> 26:24.458
Well, there is a time for spades

26:24.625 --> 26:28.921
and a time for books, no?

26:29.088 --> 26:30.380
Try again.

26:30.547 --> 26:31.632
"Lo!

26:31.799 --> 26:33.133
We shall not..."

26:37.179 --> 26:42.267
II'

26:42.434 --> 26:45.687
Lest we forget
we are on an island.

26:45.854 --> 26:49.149
You're an aficionado
of the decorative arts?

26:49.316 --> 26:52.569
I collect the decorative.

26:52.736 --> 26:55.322
It's my only vice, and secret.

26:55.489 --> 26:56.782
Hm.

26:56.949 --> 26:58.789
There are no secrets from God,
Lord Palmerston.

26:58.826 --> 27:00.953
He registers our every misdeed.

27:01.120 --> 27:03.539
Makes us pay for them.

27:06.083 --> 27:08.335
Wander what will be
the price? Of mine.

27:08.502 --> 27:11.672
1 really don't {want
